<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_f05d32dcdc2b.aspx"><b>丘中有麻</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonf05d32dcdc2b">
丘中有麻，彼留子嗟。彼留子嗟，将其来施施。<br />丘中有麦，彼留子国。彼留子国，将其来食。<br />丘中有李，彼留之子。彼留之子，贻我佩玖。
