<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_47fd02b86d28.aspx"><b>桧风·羔裘</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson47fd02b86d28">
<p>羔裘逍遥，狐裘以朝。岂不尔思？劳心忉忉。<br />羔裘翱翔，狐裘在堂。岂不尔思？我心忧伤。<br />羔裘如膏，日出有曜。岂不尔思？中心是悼。</p>
